    "description": {
      "en": {
        "provenance": "imported",
        "value": "·         Technical assistance and funding support for quality vitamin ’A’ supplementation for 6-59 months girls and boys provided and coordinated with partners biannually in all 75 districts.\r\n\r\n ·         Technical assistance and funding support for micronutrients supplementation to adolescents, pregnant and lactating women provided and coordinated with partners in Kapilvastu, Nawalparasi, Udaypur, Dang, Tanahu, Dadeldhura and Kavre districts.\r\n·         Technical assistance and funding support for MNP distribution along with IYCF promotion to 6-23 months children provided and coordinated with partners in Rupandehi, Parsa, Makanpur, Rasuwa, Gorkha and Palpa districts.\r\n.    Technical assistance and funding support for monitoring and social marketing  of adequately  iodized salt use  at household level provided and coordinated with partners in Dhanusha, Sarlahi, Mahottari, Siraha, Bara, Rautahat, Sunsari, Jhapa and Saptari districts."
      },
      "ne": null
    },
